item.description:
I know this is short notice, but anyone wanting to join me this Friday in Tewksbury for a 9 hole round is more than welcome to join me! I'm taking a half mental day from work to start the weekend, and hit the links!

I'm going to try and book the tee time for around 3pm (I can book on Wednesday with the 2 day advance rule). I'll post an update what time I was able to get.

$20 for the 9 holes, and $9 for the cart rental.

www.tewksburycc.com if you need more information.

Thanks!
Chuck
